name: We are nature and nature is us 2.0
description:
From coffee beans in your favorite beverage to large-scale mansions, there is something for everyone. The roots of trees provide us with all of the materials we need. We would be unable to develop and produce if our planet lacked all of its powers.

However, we overuse it. We don't consider the ramifications when we cut down hectares of rainforest or dry up the oceans. Everything we lose in nature we also lose in art. Every action we perform must have its own set of repercussions.

Create, be inspired, and safeguard what you have.
